### Personal Finance Manager — Sample Requests
### Compatible with: VS Code REST Client, Visual Studio, JetBrains HTTP Client, Scalar import
### Usage: Replace @categoryId / @transactionId / @budgetId with real UUIDs from previous responses

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5068
@contentType = application/json


# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  CATEGORIES                                                                  ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

### Create income category — Gehalt
# @name createGehalt
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Gehalt",
  "type": "Income"
}

###

### Create income category — Sonstiges Einkommen
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Sonstiges Einkommen",
  "type": "Income"
}

###

### Create expense category — Lebensmittel
# @name createLebensmittel
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Lebensmittel",
  "type": "Expense"
}

###

### Create expense category — Miete
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Miete",
  "type": "Expense"
}

###

### Create expense category — Transport
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Transport",
  "type": "Expense"
}

###

### Create expense category — Freizeit
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Freizeit",
  "type": "Expense"
}

###

### Get all categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories

###

### Get single category (replace ID)
@categoryId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}

###

### Update category
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Lebensmittel & Haushalt",
  "type": "Expense"
}

###

### Delete category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}


# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  TRANSACTIONS                                                                ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

### Create transaction — Gehaltseingang März
# @name createTx1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "amount": 3200.00,
  "description": "Gehalt März 2026",
  "date": "2026-03-01"
}

###

### Create transaction — Supermarkt
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "amount": 87.45,
  "description": "Billa Wocheneinkauf",
  "date": "2026-03-05"
}

###

### Create transaction — Miete
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "amount": 950.00,
  "description": "Miete März",
  "date": "2026-03-01"
}

###

### Get all transactions (no filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions

###

### Get transactions filtered by month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions?year=2026&month=3

###

### Get transactions filtered by year only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions?year=2026

###

### Get single transaction (replace ID)
@transactionId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/{{transactionId}}

###

### Update transaction
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "amount": 92.30,
  "description": "Billa Wocheneinkauf (korrigiert)",
  "date": "2026-03-05"
}

###

### Delete transaction
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/{{transactionId}}


# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  BUDGETS                                                                     ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

### Set budget — Lebensmittel März 2026
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/budgets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "year": 2026,
  "month": 3,
  "amount": 300.00
}

###

### Set budget — Miete März 2026 (upsert — creates or updates)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/budgets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "year": 2026,
  "month": 3,
  "amount": 950.00
}

###

### Set budget — Transport März 2026
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/budgets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "year": 2026,
  "month": 3,
  "amount": 80.00
}

###

### Get budgets for a specific month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/budgets?year=2026&month=3

###

### Get all budgets (no filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/budgets

###

### Delete budget (replace ID)
@budgetId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/budgets/{{budgetId}}


# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  SUMMARY                                                                     ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

### Get summary for März 2026
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/summary?year=2026&month=3

###

### Get summary for February 2026
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/summary?year=2026&month=2

###

### Get summary — missing params (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/summary


